tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished T30 at the California Qualifying Tournament, shooting rounds of 75-71-73-78. Second-round 62 at the ATB Financial Classic moved him into a T2 with Julien Brun. Finished T3 for first top 10 of the season, two strokes behind champion Daniel Miernicki.
tourBios.personal: Was in Sports Illustrated's Faces in Crowd when he was 13...Works at an accounting office...Hopes to play Augusta National someday...Is a big Denver Broncos fan...Dream foursome would include Peyton Manning, LeBron James and Tiger Woods.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T3rd in 2015 at the ATB Financial Classic.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T95th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
